+ Create Streaming Tables\nfor Ingestion
++ SQL Definition
+++_ CREATE OR REFRESH STREAMING TABLE
+++_ AS SELECT * FROM STREAM read_files(...)
+++_ STREAM keyword = incremental processing
++ Python Definition
+++_ @dp.table decorator
+++_ spark.readStream.format("cloudFiles")
+++_ Returns streaming DataFrame
-- read_files() with STREAM
---_ Auto Loader enabled automatically
---_ format => 'json' / 'csv' / etc.
---_ Pipeline manages checkpoints
-- Default Flow
